(1028, 61, 'add_country_9_content_section', '<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Egypt Tourist Visasticker visaRequirements for Indians:-</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Passport valid for at least 6 months beyond the intended stay in Egyptand minimum 3 blank pages .</li>\r\n 	<li>Two recent photos: 3.5X4.5cm, white background matt finish, 80% face size.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hotel Confirmation Vouchers on Egypt company letterhead.</li>\r\n 	<li>Day to Day Tour itinerary.</li>\r\n 	<li>Air tickets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Income tax returns or Form 16.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original bank statement for the last sixmonths with bank stamp and sign. Bank balance required a minimum Balance Rs -140000.</li>\r\n 	<li>If employed required Salary Slips for the last 3 months.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original Leave Letter from Employer/School/University.</li>\r\n 	<li>Retire proof /Pension order- if retired.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company registration proof eg. Trade License /MOA/Deed - if self-employed.</li>\r\n 	<li>If student required student id and bonafide letter.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<b>Egypt BusinessVisa Requirements for Indians:-</b>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Passport valid for at least 6 months beyond the intended stay in Egyptminimum 3 blank pages.</li>\r\n 	<li>Two recent photos: 3.5X4.5mm, white background matt finish, 80% face size.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original bank statement for the last threemonths with bank stamp and sign. Bank balance required a minimum Balance Rs-100000.</li>\r\n 	<li>Invitationletter from the business associates in Egypt.</li>\r\n 	<li>Covering letter fromIndian Company.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hotel confirmation in Egypt.</li>\r\n 	<li>last three years Income Tax Returns.</li>\r\n 	<li>Confirmed air ticket with PNR No.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<b>Please note the below requirements forEgyptTouristEVisa:</b>\r\n\r\n01. Passport Bio Data Pages\r\n\r\n02. Covering Letter on Letterhead OR If Employee NOC from Employer\r\n\r\n03. Ticket\r\n\r\n04. Hotel Confirmation\r\n\r\n05. Photo\r\n\r\n06. Covid Final Vaccination Certificate\r\n\r\nVisaFee &amp; Processing Time as Follows for Single Entry\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
