(1052, 61, 'add_country_13_content_section', 'Kindly check belowGeorgiaE-Visa Requirements:\r\n\r\n<b>E- VISA</b>\r\n01. Passport Bio Data Pages\r\n02. Recent Camera Click clear Photo\r\n03. Applicant Personal Contact No\r\n04. Ticket itinerary\r\n05. Hotel Confirmation\r\n06. Covering Letter on company Letterhead\r\n07. Company GST Registration\r\n08. Last 06 months updated bank statement with minimum balance of 01 lakh\r\n09. If Student - Student ID Card and Birth Certificate\r\n10. Spouse Marriage Certificate\r\n11. Travel Insurance.\r\n<table width=\"1200\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr valign=\"top\">\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#fafafa\" width=\"171\"><b>Processing Time</b></td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#fafafa\" width=\"1025\">05 Working Days</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#fafafa\" width=\"171\"><b>Note</b></td>\r\n<td bgcolor=\"#fafafa\" width=\"1025\"><b>Your travel document must meet the following criteria:\r\n- Its validity shall extend at least for 3 months after the validity period of requestedGeorgianvisa\r\n-Document should include not less then 2 free pages.\r\n-Should not be damaged and should not include unofficial remarks.\r\n- it should be issued within the previous 10 years.</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;'),
