(1070, 61, 'add_country_16_content_section', '<b>Israel Tourist Visa application document: -</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Passport:</b>Original Valid passport for 03months from the date of arrival in Israel.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Photo:</b>2 photographs: 5.5X5.5cm, white background matt finish . And need photo soft copy</li>\r\n 	<li>If the applicant has a Business/ companys Account, please also attach a copy\r\nof that account (for the last 4 months) and a copy of PAN Card for the company.</li>\r\n 	<li>TravelTicket Booking (NOT CONFIRMED TICKET)</li>\r\n 	<li>If Employee NOC from the place of work for yourtravel(In Original) + 4months pay slip.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Traveland Medical insurance</b>with COVID Coverage.</li>\r\n 	<li>TourProgram (Day-to-Day Itinerary) including Hotel Reservation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original personal Bank statement for 6 months with bank stamp and sing .</li>\r\n 	<li>Aadhar Card Copy.</li>\r\n 	<li>Last 03 Years ITR.</li>\r\n 	<li>If self Employed Company GST Registration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>IMPORTANT REMARKS</b>\r\n1. If applicant has entry /exit stamp for any one of the following countries with the valid\r\nvisas (in the last 3 years from the date of submission of application): USA/ Canada/\r\nSchengen/ Australia.\r\nIn addition, if the applicant has the visa/s toIsraelthat has been used (Entry/ Exit\r\nstamp) in the past 3 years from the date of submission of application.\r\nThen Bank statement/ Flight ticket /Salary slip/ Hotel Booking- NOT required.\r\n\r\n2. Submit all the above mentioned documents Only in A4 size and not in back to back\r\nformat.\r\n3. IN CASE OF MINOR ACCOMPANYING PARENTS: -\r\na) Need original Birth Certificate with Apostille (attested by MEA).\r\nb) Parents (Father &amp; Mother) need to visit IVP at the time of Submission for\r\nsigning the Minor consent form.\r\nc) In case one of the parents is not in India then he/ she must sign the Minor\r\nconsent form at Embassy ofIsraelin that particular country.\r\n4. The Embassy may ask for additional documents or requests for the Interview.\r\n\r\n5. While submitting theISRAELVFS Can ask for any additional document.\r\n\r\n<b>ISRAELVISA PROCESSING TIME 10-15WORKING DAYS.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
