(1154, 61, 'add_country_30_content_section', 'We are one of the<b>BestRussia Tourist visa agent in Kolkata</b>.<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">JET TOUR &amp; TRAVELS </span>Visateam will help you to prepare your entire documents for Russia Visa. We arrange Hotel voucher from Russia travels agent(in Russian language). We provide end to end visa consultancy services .\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><b>Russia Visa Requirements for Indians:</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Original passport 6 months validity.</li>\r\n 	<li>2 ps colour photographs 3.5 x 4.5 face size 80% .</li>\r\n 	<li>Hotel voucher from Russia travels agent(in Russian language)registered with the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Russian Federation .</li>\r\n 	<li>Air ticket ( if avlabel ).</li>\r\n 	<li>To know more, call or whatapp our Visa experts at <b>(+91) 9088105966</b> , Email id : <b>jettour.infotravels@gmail.com</b>.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<u><b>Russia Visa prossing steps:-</b></u>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>All original documents requiredas per above check list.</li>\r\n 	<li>Our visa expert review all documents and apply Russia visa.</li>\r\n 	<li>Make the payment to our Bank account or Google pay number.</li>\r\n 	<li>Get yourvisa whithin 2 to 7 working daysas per visa category .</li>\r\n</ol>'),
