(1208, 61, 'add_country_39_content_section', '<u><b>Thailand Tourist Visa Requirements:</b></u>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Original passport with 06 Months validity.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bank statement for last six months with stamp and signature 60000 RS metering balance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Confirmed roundtrip air tickets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Hotel reservation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Two ps recentphotographs 3.5 x 4.5 cm size white background photo 80% Face Size.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<b>Visa Documents required for Thailand Transit Visa:</b>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><b>Passport:</b>Original passport with 06 Months validity from the date of travel.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Photographs</b>: Tworecent photographs3.5 x 4.5 size background white.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Proof of transportation:</b>a) Ticket confirmationin and out of Thailand.b) Cruise confirmation in and out of Thailand.</li>\r\n 	<li><b>Evidence of adequate finance</b>: Bank statement for last month with stamp and signature updated with minimum balance equally as 700 USD/person or copy of credit card bill issued by a bank last month.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;'),
