(1226, 61, 'add_country_42_content_section', '<b>Visa Documents for UK Tourist Visa:</b>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Original passport with 06 Months validity from the date of travel. + Old Passports if any.</li>\r\n 	<li>Covering letter mentioning your travel details and stay details while in the UK.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original Bank statement for last 6 months updated with healthy and sufficient balance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Income tax / Form 16 for the last 3 years.</li>\r\n 	<li>Salary Slips for last 6 months - if employed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Original Leave letter from employer/school/college.</li>\r\n 	<li>Retirement Letter if retired</li>\r\n 	<li>School / College ID proof - if student.</li>\r\n 	<li>Retirement proof eg. pension passbook/slips if retired.</li>\r\n 	<li>Other financial papers NSC, PPF, Bonds, FD, share property papers, etc.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<u><b>Documentsif Invited by Friends/Family:</b></u>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><b>Passport &amp;Visacopies.</b></li>\r\n 	<li><b>Invitation letter.</b></li>\r\n 	<li><b>Bank statements for last 3months updated. - if sponsoring.</b></li>\r\n 	<li><b>Salary slips for last 3 months.- if sponsoring.</b></li>\r\n 	<li><b>Rent Agreement.</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;'),
