(1238, 61, 'add_country_44_content_section', 'VIETNAM TOURIST VISA REQUIRED DOCUMENT:\r\n\r\n1) 2 Photo (recent camera click photo white background 70% Face size ).\r\n\r\n2) Passport Bio Data Pages.\r\n\r\n3) If earlier Travelled toVietnamSend Visa Copy\r\n\r\n4) Applicant Personal Contact No.\r\n\r\n5) Ticket with exact dates. (Embassy issuing visas as per ticket only)\r\n\r\n6) Hotel Confirmation.'),
